{"tid":1991714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係講笑, 施多夫係被嚴重低估既中場","createTime":"2020-04-27T15:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T04:57:00.000Z","uid":34571,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"80b956d9b5ba62131e2ff1e53a6e64506fc022cd","tid":1991714,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"首先佢拎過四次歐聯, 分別係阿積士, 皇馬, 米蘭, 史上唯一一個係三隊球隊都拎過歐聯<br />\n講返佢特點, 黑人黎講佢係非常有腦, 去到米蘭變完全體, 係米蘭打過攻中, 中中, 到後尾客串防中都無問題, 最後尾細哨同佢爭正選都失敗咗, 佢仲係非常穩陣.<br />\n<br />\n之後到遠射, 對於中場黎講, 有遠射係會加好多分, 而施多夫遠射直頭強項, 係皇馬既雷獸射球大家到依家都印象好深, 佢係米蘭仲有處罰球, 質素都好好.<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 佢身體質素好好, 可能因為佢黑人關系, 身位好好, 護球勁, 盤扭助攻樣樣有<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/narpennklmc31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2Fnarpennklmc31.jpg&h=aec7171c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19年<br />\n<br />\n球王片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDxiIlBhdbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsDxiIlBhdbI&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Te9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=1fa6c154\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDxiIlBhdbI</a>"},{"pid":"b12334775c851fb98877ff7869c9b88c20eb1ea6","tid":1991714,"uid":34571,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/narpennklmc31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fnarpennklmc31.jpg&h=10d09d77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e47a2bb3851c08e5bfa5b28725c7425b49b01fe5","tid":1991714,"uid":34571,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"生涯數據: 上陣867 入球128 助攻117"},{"pid":"0e66ffffac2c8b03c67feb69c8a2cbe9ad2edd34","tid":1991714,"uid":61577,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"其實中場同籃球控衛一樣，你冇位分波仲可以遠射先有人忌憚你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce16ea11b441910c763ab8aa84590c10f29a9e53"